# Rails services

Read `docs/standards/stacks/rails8/technical-guideline.md` §3 for full detail.

- One use case per service object; open transaction boundary here
- Context namespacing when architecture mode is `ddd` (e.g. `Billing::RecordUsage`)
- Delegate domain logic to models/aggregates; no HTTP or rendering concerns
